    Howard Armstrong</A>, <A HREF="http://www.invent.org/book/book-text/30.html">Lee
    DeForest</A>, <A HREF="http://www.invent.org/book/book-text/41.html">Philo
    Taylor Farnsworth</A>, <A HREF="http://www.invent.org/book/book-text/111.html">Vladimir
    Kosmar Zworykin</A>
    <LI><A HREF="http://homepage.seas.upenn.edu/~lzeltser/radio/">Early Stages
    of Soviet and American Radio Broadcasting</A>
    <LI><A HREF="http://www.mediahistory.com/teevee.html">The Media History
